category = Category.create(name: %Q^Kindergarten/First Grade^);
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is enthusiastic about learning new topics. He/she enjoys working with Center activities. However, %s needs to gain more self-control.^, spanish: %Q^%s esta entusiamado en aprender sobre nuevos temas. el/Ella disfruta trabajar con los Centros de actividades. Sin embargo, %s necesita obtener mas control de si mismo.^, chinese: %Q^%s熱心学习新題目。他/她享受中心活动。无论如何,%s需要培养自我控制能力。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is a very talented artist. He/she works very hard and is speaking English more.^, spanish: %Q^%s es un artista bien talentoso. El/Ella trabaja bien duro y esta hablando el Ingles mas a menudo.^, chinese: %Q^%s是一位很有天份的艺术家。他/她非常勤奋和已多说些英語。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is very quiet and shy. He/she tries to complete his/her work independently.^, spanish: %Q^%s es bien callado/a y timido/a. El/ella trata de completar su trabajo independientemente.^, chinese: %Q^他/她比較文靜和害羞。他/她尝試独立完成功課。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s has adjusted to school nicely. He/she understands the routines and tries to follow along. I am trying to get him/her to speak more.^, spanish: %Q^%s se ha ajustado a la escuela muy bien. El/ella entiende las rutinas y trata de seguir con todos. Estoy tratando que el/ella hable mas.^, chinese: %Q^%s已适应學校生活。他/她明白课堂常规并尝试跟随。我会引导他/她多說英語。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s loves exploring new topics. %s is always willing to share his/her thoughts.^, spanish: %Q^%s ama explorar nuevos temas . %s siempre esta dispuesto ha compartir sus pensamientos.^, chinese: %Q^%s喜愛探索新題目。%s也经常愿意分享自己的见解。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis an excellent reader. He/she enjoys writing stories and shares them with the class.^, spanish: %Q^%s es un lector excelente . El/ella disfruta escribir historias y las comparte con la clase.^, chinese: %Q^%s是一位优秀的读者。他/她喜好写故事并与同学们分享。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s tries very hard. However, he/she needs more help. Please make sure that %s does homework every night and practices letters and words every night.^, spanish: %Q^%s trata muy duro. Sin embargo, el/ella necesita mas ayuda. Por favor de asegurarse que %s haga su tarea todas las noches y practique sus letras y palabras todas las noche.^, chinese: %Q^%s很努力。但是，他/她需要帮助。請确保%s每晚做家庭作业并练习字母和单词。。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis eager to try new things and is willing to share what he/she has learned.^, spanish: %Q^%s esta ansioso/a de tratar cosas nueva y dispuesto/a ha compartir lo que el/ella ha aprendido.^, chinese: %Q^%s喜愛尝试事物并分享他/她所學的。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^I am working with %s to get him/her to share thoughts and opinions.^, spanish: %Q^Yo estoy trabajando con %s para conseguir que el/ella comparta sus pensamientos y opiniones.^, chinese: %Q^我在教导%s来让他/她怎樣分享他/她的见解和意見。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s needs to pay more attention and to focus on directions.^, spanish: %Q^%s necesita poner mas atencion y enfocarse en las direcciones.^, chinese: %Q^%s需要专心和注意听从指示。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is always willing to help classmates.^, spanish: %Q^%s siempre esta dispuesto/a ayudar ha sus companeros.^, chinese: %Q^%s時常幫助同學。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s enjoys writing stories. %s needs help with letters and sounds.^, spanish: %Q^%s disfruta escribir historias. %s necesita ayuda con las letras y sonidos.^, chinese: %Q^%s喜欢写故事。%s在字母和字母发音上需要帮助。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is a bright and inquisitive child. %s likes science and enjoys doing experiments.^, spanish: %Q^%s es un/a nino/a brillante y curioso. %s le encanta la ciencia y disfruta hacer experimentos.^, chinese: %Q^%s是一位聰明和好奇的孩子。%s喜愛自然科學和做实验。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s works hard and is doing well. %s enjoys reading and learns new words easily.^, spanish: %Q^%s trabaja duro y esta haciendo bien. %s disfruta leer y aprende palabras nueva facilmente.^, chinese: %Q^%s努力学习并在学习上做得好。%s喜愛阅读和學习新单词容易上手。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis not being consistent in their homework.It is important that he/she put the same amount of time and effort into their homework as they do in their classwork in order to improve.^, spanish: %Q^%sno es consistente en sus tareas. Es importante que el/ella ponga el mismo esfuerzo y tiempo en sus tareas, como lo hace en los trabajos que hacemos en la escuela, para asi poder mejorar.^, chinese: %Q^%s没有時常做功課。重要的是，他/她要象在做课堂功课花费一样多时间和努力来完成家庭作业。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s tries hard when he/she is in school. However, he/she has missed a great deal of school. %s must come to school every day.^, spanish: %Q^%s trata duro cuando el/ella esta en la escuela. Sin embargo, el/ella ha esta perdiendo tiempo de ensenaza. %s tiene que venir a la escuela todos los dias.^, chinese: %Q^%s在校勤奋好學。但是,他/她缺席很多天。%s必须每天都来上課。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^I am extremely concerned about %s absences. Please see me.^, spanish: %Q^Yo estoy muy preocupado sobre las asusencias de %s. Por favor de verme.^, chinese: %Q^我非常担心%s的缺席。請來見我。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is often late to school. Please make sure that %s is here at 8:50 every day.^, spanish: %Q^%s,A menudo llega tarde ha la escuela. Por favor de asegurarse de que %s este aqui en la escuela a las 8:50 todos los dias.^, chinese: %Q^%s時常迟到。請确定%s每天按时在早上8點50分来校上课。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s frequently falls asleep in class. Please make sure that %s gets to bed by 8:00.^, spanish: %Q^%s frecuentemente se duerme en las clase. Por favor de asegurarse que %s se acueste ha las 8:00pm.^, chinese: %Q^%s時常在堂上睡覺。請确保%s每晚8点按时上床睡觉。^)
category = Category.create(name: %Q^Reading^);
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is reading at a Level %s which is above grade level.^, spanish: %Q^%s esta leyendo al nivel %s que esta sobre su nivel.^, chinese: %Q^%s的阅读程度是%s，超过年级的程度。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s clearly enjoying reading and reads for sustained periods of time.^, spanish: %Q^Claramente %s disfruta las lecturas y lee por un tiempos sustancial.^, chinese: %Q^%s喜愛阅读和能阅读很長時間。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s talks about a variety of topics with his/her partners.^, spanish: %Q^%s habla sobre una variedad de temas con su pareja en el salon de clase.^, chinese: %Q^%s跟他/她的伙伴谈论不同的題材。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%stakes notes while reading and is able to use these notes to talk about books.^, spanish: %Q^%s toma apuntes mientras el/ella lee. %s es capaz de usar esos apuntes para hablar sobre el libro.^, chinese: %Q^%s在阅读时记笔记并运用自己的笔記来进行討論。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is reading at a Level %s which is at grade level.^, spanish: %Q^%s esta leyendo al nivel %s que es, el nivel que debe de estar leyendo.^, chinese: %Q^%s的阅读程度是%s达到年级的程度。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s enjoys reading and talking with classmates about what he/she has read.^, spanish: %Q^%s disfruta leer y hablar con sus companeros sobre lo que el/ella leyo.^, chinese: %Q^%s喜愛阅读并跟同學讨论他/她所看的书本的內容。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s reads fluently and with expression.^, spanish: %Q^%s lee con fluidez y con expresion.^, chinese: %Q^%s阅读流利和读出感情。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is reading at a Level %s which is below grade level. Please make sure that %s reads at least %s minutes every night.^, spanish: %Q^%s lee al nivel %s que esta por debajo su nivel de grado. Por favor de asugurarse que %s lea por lo menos %s minutos todas las noches.^, chinese: %Q^%s的阅读程度是%s低于年级程度。請确保%s每晚必须最少阅读%s分钟。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is easily distracted during reading. We are working on reading for longer periods of time.^, spanish: %Q^%s se distrae facilmente durante lectura. Estamos trabajando para que pueda leer por periodo mas largo de tiempo.^, chinese: %Q^%s在阅读时容易分心。我們在学习怎样阅读较长的时间。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis currently on %slevel and has moved up%sreading levels since September.^, spanish: %Q^%sesta en el %snivel y ha subido al%snivel de lectura desde septiembre.^, chinese: %Q^%s现在的阅读程度是%s从九月开始已提高了%s阅读程度。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^Although%sparticipates and shares ideas in patner and small group conversation,%s needs to participate more in whole class conversations.^, spanish: %Q^Aunque%sparticipa y comparte sus ideas con su companero y en grupos pequenos de conversacion,%snecesita participar mas en las conversaciones con la clase entera.^, chinese: %Q^雖然%s跟伙伴和小組分享自己的见解,%s也需要多些參与全班的讨论。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s clearly enjoys reading and reads for sustained periods of time across a variety of genres^, spanish: %Q^%s Claramente disfruta la lectura y lee por un periodo sustancial de tiempo en varios generos.^, chinese: %Q^%s热爱阅读并在不同题材的书籍上能够阅读较长的时间^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is making progress towards talking and writing about his/her books.^, spanish: %Q^%s Esta haciendo progreso hacia hablar y escribir acerca de sus libros.^, chinese: %Q^%s在叙述和写有关概括书本內容有进步。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis able to engage in conversations about his/her books with the support of a teacher.^, spanish: %Q^%s Es capaz de conversar acerca de sus libros con ayuda del maestro.^, chinese: %Q^在老师的教导下%s可以交談有关他/她所看的书本的內容。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s has been stopping more often while he/she is reading to jot down his/her ideas.^, spanish: %Q^%s Esta parando mas seguido mientras el/ella esta leyendo para anotar sus ideas.^, chinese: %Q^%s已经能時常在阅读时停下来，并写下他/她的见解。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s independently stops to think and write about his/her reading.^, spanish: %Q^%s Para independientemente para pensar y escribir sobre su lectura.^, chinese: %Q^%s可以独立停下来，思考并写下他/她所读的内容。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In reading, he/she recognizes her sight words.^, spanish: %Q^En lectura, reconoce las palabras de alta frecuencia.^, chinese: %Q^在阅读上，他/她认识常用的单词。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In reading, he/she makes sure she understands what she’s reading.^, spanish: %Q^En lectura, se asegura que entiende lo que esta leyendo.^, chinese: %Q^在閱讀上，他/她确保明白所读的內容。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^When he gets to a tricky word, he uses strategies that we’ve learned in class.^, spanish: %Q^Cuando llega a una palabra dificil, usa estrategias que hemos aprendido en la clase.^, chinese: %Q^当他遇到困難的单詞时，他应用在班上所學的方法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^When he/she gets to a tricky word, she should think of a word that makes sense^, spanish: %Q^Cuando llega a una palabra dificil, debe pensar en una palabra que tenga sentido,^, chinese: %Q^當他/她遇到困難的单詞时，她应該想想这个单词在這里是否适合。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He/she should practice sight words.^, spanish: %Q^Tiene que practicar sus palabras de alta frecuencia.^, chinese: %Q^他/她应该练习常用的单词。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^When he finishes a book, he should touch the pages and say what happened in his own words.^, spanish: %Q^Cuando termine un libro, debe tocar las paginas y decir lo que paso en sus propias palabras^, chinese: %Q^當他讀完一本書，他應該按著每頁并概述發生了什么事情。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In reading, she sounds like the characters when she reads.^, spanish: %Q^En lectura, ella suena como los personajes cuando esta leyendo.^, chinese: %Q^在阅读上，在她阅读时，她的語音应象故事中的人物。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^She should make sure to read through the whole word, especially the end.^, spanish: %Q^En lectura, debe leer la palabra entera, especialmente el final.^, chinese: %Q^她应該确定读整個单词，尤其是单词的最后部分。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^When she gets to a tricky word, she should try something^, spanish: %Q^Cuando llegue a una palabra dificil, debe intentar algo.^, chinese: %Q^當她遇到困難的单词時，她应該尝試其它方法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^After he reads a book, he should retell the most important words in his words.^, spanish: %Q^Despues de leer un libro, debe redecir las cosas mas importantes de la historia con sus propias palabras.^, chinese: %Q^在他读完一本书后，他应該用自己的词汇來敘述重要的词汇。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He should make sure to think about what’s happening in the story when he reads.^, spanish: %Q^Debe estar seguro de pensar acerca de lo que esta pasando en la historia cuando lee.^, chinese: %Q^在他阅读時，他应該想想故事发生了什么。^)
category = Category.create(name: %Q^Writing^);
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is a strong, creative writer who enjoys writing.^, spanish: %Q^%ses un escritor capacitado y creativo que le encanta escribir^, chinese: %Q^%s是一位富有創造力的作家并喜愛写作。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is a strong writer who applies all the new skills we have taught into his/her writing.^, spanish: %Q^%ses un escritor capacitado que aplica todas la nuevas habilidades en sus composiciones.^, chinese: %Q^%s是一位強壮的作者和运用我们所教导他/她所有的新的写作方法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is able to reread his/her work and revise the writing to make it better.^, spanish: %Q^%ses capaz de releer y revisar sus composiciones sin dificultad para mejorar lo escrito .^, chinese: %Q^%s能够重讀和修改自己的作品来改良。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%shas difficulty getting his/her ideas on to the paper.^, spanish: %Q^%stiene dificultades en poner sus ideas en papel.^, chinese: %Q^%s在书面上有困難表达他/她的见解。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s has greatly improved in writing. He/she can write for the entire period.^, spanish: %Q^%sa mejorado bastante en su escritura. El/ella puede escribir durante todo el periodo.^, chinese: %Q^%s在写作上进步很大，他/她能够整节课坚持写作。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sdoes not enjoy writing. During this time, %s talks to classmates.^, spanish: %Q^%sNo le gusta escribir. Durante este tiempo,%shabla con sus compañeros del salón.^, chinese: %Q^%s不喜愛寫作。%s。上课时,%s与同学讲話。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%shas a strong voice when writing and makes clear his/her feelings and opinions.^, spanish: %Q^%stiene una opinion fuerte y es claro cuando escribe acerca de sus sentimientos y pensamientos.^, chinese: %Q^%s在写作时，能够清亮大声和清楚地表达他/她的感受和意見。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%sis developing writing skills and habits. %s is working on organizing his/her ideas and coming up with a clear plan for writing and seeing the difference between important and unimportant details.^, spanish: %Q^%sesta desarrollando habilidades y habitos de escribir.%sesta trabajando en organizar sus ideas y desarrollar un plan claro para escribir y observar la diferencia entre detalles importantes y otros sin importancia.^, chinese: %Q^%s逐漸发展写作的技能和习惯。%s正學习整理他/她的思維和把重要和不重要的細节分开。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is able to come up with his/her ideas for his/her pieces independently and has grown much more confident as a writer.^, spanish: %Q^%s Es capaz de traer su ideas con sus piezas de forma independiente y ha crecido muchos como escritor^, chinese: %Q^%s在写作上能夠独立地构思他/她的写作題纲，并逐漸在写作上更有自信。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In writing, she does a good job of planning her stories before she writes them^, spanish: %Q^En escritura, hace un buen trabajo de planear su historia antes de escribir.^, chinese: %Q^在写作上，在写作之前，她在計划写她的故事方面上做得十分好。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In writing, he does a good job of applying the strategies that we’re learning in class.^, spanish: %Q^En escritura, hace un buen trabajo de aplicar las estrategias a sus propias historias.^, chinese: %Q^在写作上，他在应用在班上所學的方法上做得非常好。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In writing, she does a good job of using her knowledge of sight words.^, spanish: %Q^En escritura, hace un buen trabajo y usa su conocimiento de palabras de alta frecuencia.^, chinese: %Q^在写作上，她在应用所认识的常用单词方面做得好。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^She does a good job of writing stories with a beginning, middle and end.^, spanish: %Q^Hace un buen trabajo de escribir historias con un principio, medio y final.^, chinese: %Q^她在写故事的开头、中间和結尾上做得十分好。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^She should use the strategies that we’ve learned to add more (dialogue, feelings).^, spanish: %Q^Debe usar las estrategias que hemos aprendido para elaborar (como los personajes se sienten y lo que dicen).^, chinese: %Q^她应該应用所学的方法在写作上加入(对話、感受)。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In writing, he should practice stretching out tricky words by sliding his finger and writing the first, middle and last sounds he hears.^, spanish: %Q^Cuando escriba una palabra dificil, debe decir la palabra lentamente, y escribir el primer, medio y ultimo sonido.^, chinese: %Q^在写作上，他应該练习用手指，指着困難的单词慢慢读出来，并写下他所听到的单詞的第一個、中間和最后的发音。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^She should continue to add details to her pictures to help tell the story.^, spanish: %Q^Ella debe continuar agregando mas detalles en sus dibujos para ayudar a contar su historia mejor.^, chinese: %Q^她应該坚持在故事的图画上加上細节来帮助叙述故事。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^She should work on writing stories with a beginning, middle and ending.^, spanish: %Q^Ella debe trabajar en los escritos de historias con un principio, un medio y final.^, chinese: %Q^她应該在写作的开头、中间和結尾上加強。^)
category = Category.create(name: %Q^Math^);
