Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is below grade level in math.^, spanish: %Q^%s esta bajo el nivel de grado en matematicas.^, chinese: %Q^%s的数学低于年级的程度。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s is able to explain his/her thinking both verbally and in written form.^, spanish: %Q^%s es capas de explicar como el/ella piensa en forma verbal y escrito.^, chinese: %Q^%s能夠在口头上和书面上解释他/她的想法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s has difficulty explaining his/her thinking.^, spanish: %Q^%s tiene dificultades para explicar lo que el/ella piensa.^, chinese: %Q^%s有困難解释他/她的想法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s needs to practice number facts every night.^, spanish: %Q^%s necesita practicar los factores numericos todas las noches.^, chinese: %Q^%s需要每晚練习數字的因數。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^Encourage %s to draw pictures to help solve word problems.^, spanish: %Q^Animelo %s ha dibujar para que le ayude a resolver problemas de palabra.^, chinese: %Q^請鼓励%s画图案来帮助解答应用題。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^%s continues to display strong skills during small group work in math.^, spanish: %Q^%s continua ensenando fuertes habilidades durante grupos pequenos en matematicas.^, chinese: %Q^%s在数学小组上，继续表现出在数学上巩固的技能。^)
