Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^We are working with %s on finding more efficient strategies in our current unit.^, spanish: %Q^Estamos trabajando con%s en encontra mas eficientes estrategias en nuestra unidad.^, chinese: %Q^我们正在学习%s，我们现时的单元是找出更多的有效方法。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^In math, she uses effective strategies to see how many (counting by 5, 10, doubles).^, spanish: %Q^En matemáticas, usa estrategias efectivas para ver cuantas hay (contando de 5, 10 y dobles) .^, chinese: %Q^在数学上，她应用有效的方法來算出答案(进5,进10,的倍數)。^)
