Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He knows how to count by 2, 5’s and 10’s.^, spanish: %Q^Sabe contar pos 2’s, 5 and 10’s.^, chinese: %Q^他知道进2、进5和进10数数。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He does a great job of counting on (5 and 3 more makes 8).^, spanish: %Q^Hace un buen trabajo de contar adelante (5 y 3 mas hacen diez).^, chinese: %Q^他在向前数数計算上(5加上3等于8)做得好。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He already knows his doubles.^, spanish: %Q^Ya sabe sus dobles.^, chinese: %Q^他已經知道倍數。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He should work on using more effective strategies to see how many with the rekenrek.^, spanish: %Q^Debe practicar usando estrategias mas efectivas para ver cuantos hay con el rekenrek.^, chinese: %Q^他应該加強应用有效地的方法來算出算盤上的數。^)
Phrase.create(category_id: category.id, english: %Q^He should practice counting by 2’s, 5’s and 10’s.^, spanish: %Q^Debe practicar contando de 2’s, 5 y 10’s^, chinese: %Q^他应該练习进2、进5和进10的数数。^)
